<div class="text-center" style="margin-top: 200px;">
    <h2 class="custom-heading">Warning Signs Your Current Structure Has Reached Its Limits</h2>

</div>

<div class="container">
    <h5 style="margin:20px;" class="text-primary">Do you feel like your company is working harder but achieving less? These symptoms might be familiar:</h5>


    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <br />

            <ul>
                <li><strong>Slow Decision-Making:</strong> Ideas and approvals get stuck in multiple layers of bureaucracy, causing you to lose valuable market opportunities.</li>
                <li><strong>Role & Responsibility Overlap:</strong> Employees are unclear on who is responsible for what, leading to duplicated efforts, dropped tasks, and frustrated teams.</li>
                <li><strong>Declining Productivity:</strong> Teams spend more time navigating internal issues and coordinating tasks than focusing on customer service and innovation.</li>
                <li>
                    <strong>Difficulty Scaling:</strong> Every attempt to grow increases operational chaos, and you feel that your current processes cannot handle the next stage of success.
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="~/img/competency.jpg" class="w-100" style="height:300px; border-radius:50px;" />
        </div>
        <div class="text-center my-5">
            <h4 class="text-primary">These are not people problems; they are symptoms of an outdated organizational structure. <br /> Ignoring them is like adding new floors to a cracked foundation. </h4>
        </div>
    </div>


</div>

<hr class="mb-5" />

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="text-center mt-5">International Expertise, Locally Endorsed:<br /> Your Certified Partner for Structural Transformation</h1>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="text-center my-3">
            <strong>Restructuring your company is a strategic decision that requires a partner<br /> with more than just theoretical knowledge. Here’s what makes our approach unique and trusted:</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/img/competency.jpg" class="w-100" />
            <div class="text-center mt-3">
                <strong class="text-primary  my-3">Accredited Strategic Partnership: Unmatched Credibility</strong>
                <p class="mt-3 mb-1">
                    We are not just another consultancy firm; we are an accredited and endorsed partner of two of the most prestigious entities:
                </p>
                <div class="text-start">
                    <ul>
                        <li>The European Bank for Reconstruction and Development (EBRD)</li>
                        <li>The Federation of Egyptian Industries (FEI)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>This partnership means our methodologies and processes have been vetted and approved against the highest international and local standards, giving you absolute confidence in the quality of service you will receive.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/img/competency.jpg" class="w-100" />
            <div class="text-center mt-3">
                <strong class="text-primary  my-3">Custom-Designed Solutions, Not Off-the-Shelf Templates</strong>
                <p style="margin-top:10px;">
                    Custom-Designed Solutions, Not Off-the-Shelf Templates<br />
                    ​A generic template can never solve a unique challenge. We start by deeply immersing ourselves in your world to build bespoke solutions. This involves: deep diagnostics of your goals and culture, co-designing the new structure in collaborative workshops, and creating a detailed blueprint that perfectly aligns with your needs. This ensures the final structure is an ideal fit, designed with your company, not just for it.
                </p>
               
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <img src="~/img/competency.jpg" class="w-100" />
            <div class="text-center mt-3">
                <strong class="text-primary  my-3">A Holistic Approach: Structure, Policies, and People</strong>
                <p class="mt-4 mb-1">
                    We believe a successful structure is one that serves its people, not the other way around. Therefore, we don't just draw org charts; we work to:
                </p>
                <div class="text-start">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Clarify Roles & Responsibilities (Job Descriptions & KPIs)</li>
                        <li>Develop & Update Policies & Procedures</li>
                        <li>Align the Structure with Your Talent Strategy</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <p>We connect the company's physical structure with its human capital to ensure the transformation is both sustainable and effective.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>

